    "description": {
      "value": "<p>They do not belong in your garden, tear them out by the roots. You can initiate this counter in response to an attack being made against you or an ally. If you are wielding a melee weapon, the foe or the ally must be within your reach. If you are wielding a ranged weapon, the foe or the ally must be within your weapon's first range increment. Make a Knowledge (nature) check against a DC equal to the foe's attack roll. If you succeed, the attack is negated and you may tear off any number of sprout stacks from the target.</p>"
